The paper also involves the creation of a large-scale data set, which could fall under the Machine Learning (cs.LG) category. 

Information Retrieval (cs.IR) could also be a possible category as the paper discusses the evaluation of various data-driven algorithms. 

Multimedia (cs.MM) could be another possible category as remote sensing images are a type of multimedia data. 

Finally, Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) could also be a possible category as the paper discusses the use of machine learning-based methods for scene classification.
